nodes.text: Battle in the Ringali Nebula junkyard

A battle occurred in a debris field near Sissubo when the Imperial II-class Star Destroyer Overseer attacked the Nadiri fleet that protected the crippled prototype battleship Starhawk, while it was enroute to the Chandrila system. As a result, Galactic Empire managed to redirect the New Republic into the Ringali Nebula.
